---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    This is a collection of notes, implementations, and explorations in machine
    learning and natural language processing. I write to learn, and I publish to
    keep myself honest.
  </p>

  <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Paper breakdowns and implementations</li>
    <li>Concepts explained from scratch</li>
    <li>Code walkthroughs with linked GitHub repos</li>
    <li>Research notes and observations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why "token by token"?</h2>
  <p>
    Because that's how language models generate text, and that's how learning
    works &mdash; one piece at a time.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you spot an error or want to discuss something, feel free to reach out.
    Corrections are welcome.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
